html:
Product Brief: Savings Account

Company : Federal bank

USP:

Discover the power of smart saving with our High-Yield Savings Account. Earn competitive interest rates and watch your savings grow effortlessly. Open your account online today and start your financial journey with us!

Campaign Objective:

Drive new account openings for the High-Yield Savings Account through online channels.

Types of Assets: Static: Yes Video: No Carousel: No

Note:

  • 1. Quick and easy online account opening with just a few clicks.
  • 2. High annual interest rate of 1.75%.
  • 3. No monthly maintenance fees.
  • 4. Access to online banking and mobile app for account management.
  • 5. Minimum initial deposit of Rs.1,000.
  • 6. FDIC insured up to Rs.250,000 per account.
  • 7. Account available for individuals aged 18 and above.

Key Planning Pointers: Age Group: 18-65 Gender: M & F

Geo Focus: Nationwide

Media Mix or Preferred Platform (Fixed/ROS/RON): Publishers: Yes/No - Yes

Affiliates: Yes/No - Yes

Device Mix (Desktop: Mobile Ratio): Optimized for both desktop and mobile.

html:
Product brief: Credit Card Promotion

Company : Federal bank

USP:

Introducing our new Platinum Rewards Credit Card! Get ready to experience unmatched benefits, from cashback on everyday spending to exclusive travel perks, all with zero annual fees. Apply online now and enjoy the convenience of a digital card!

Campaign Objective:

Promote the Platinum Rewards Credit Card and encourage online applications.

Types of Assets: Static: Yes Video: Yes Carousel: Yes

Note:

  • 1. Fast and paperless online application process.
  • 2. Credit limit based on applicant's credit score.
  • 3. Cardholders receive 2% cashback on grocery shopping and 1% on all other purchases.
  • 4. Zero annual fee for the first year.
  • 5. Interest-free grace period of up to 50 days.
  • 6. Exclusive travel discounts and access to airport lounges.
  • 7. Foreign transaction fee of 2.5% applies.
  • 8. Minimum age for application: 21 years.

Key Planning Pointers: Age Group: 21-65 Gender: M & F

Geo Focus: Nationwide

Media Mix or Preferred Platform (Fixed/ROS/RON): Publishers: Yes/No - Yes

Affiliates: Yes/No - Yes

Device Mix (Desktop: Mobile Ratio): Optimized for both desktop and mobile.

html:
Product brief: Personal loan Company : Federal bank

USP:

The Digital Platform https://personalloan.federalbank.co.in/#/entry is an end-to-end digital platform which enables the interested prospects to avail personal loans for their various needs in the best ROIs. The digital platform analyses the proposal and bases on the codes and credit policies the eligible loan amount, ROI will be automatically calculated, and the disbursement of loan can be done in just few clicks.

Campaign Objective: Disbursement of Personal Loans to NTB and ETB through the digital personal loan portal

Types of Assets: Static: yes Video:yes Carousel:yes

Note:

  • 1. No manual documentation. Only e-sign of loan documents through Aadhar OTP
  • 2. Loan amount up to Rs. 5 Lacs
  • 3. Maximum loan amount is arrived through bureau data / salary statement of the customer
  • 4. Loan tenure ranges from 12 months to 60 months depending on the profile of the customer.
  • 5. Interest rates ranges between 11.99% to 17.49%, fixed throughout the tenure of the loan.
  • 6. Processing Fee collected is 2% of the loan amount plus GST.
  • 7. Pre-closure charge is collected at 3% of the outstanding balance + GST

Key planning pointers

Age Group: 25-55, only salaried customers Gender: M &F

Geo Focus: Pin codes attached.

Media Mix or Preferred Platform (Fixed/ROS/RON):

Publishers: Yes/No : yes Affiliates: Yes/No : yes

Device Mix (Desktop: Mobile ratio):
